data.description: Discover the epitome of modern living in this stunning 2019-built home nestled on a sprawling corner lot, boasting one of the largest plots in the community. The outdoor oasis invites you to savor every moment with its built-in BBQ, creating a perfect setting for gatherings and memories. Step inside to find a kitchen adorned with luxurious granite countertops, complemented by an elegant backsplash and the warm glow of recessed lighting. The open layout creates a seamless flow, enhancing the sense of space and connectivity. This home embraces the allure of sleek tile floors throughout the entirety, with the exception of one single room. This is more than a residence; it's a statement of style, comfort, and sophisticated design. Welcome to a haven where modern conveniences and timeless aesthetics unite harmoniously. WELCOME HOME!
